Places Details Response Body

type: object

Field Required Type Description
candidates required Array<Place>

Contains an array of Place candidates.

Place Search requests return a subset of the fields that are returned by Place Details requests. If the field you want is not returned by Place Search, you can use Place Search to get a place_id, then use that Place ID to make a Place Details request.

See Place for more information.
status required PlacesStatus

Contains metadata on the request.

See PlacesStatus for more information.

error_message optional string

Contains additional information about the request.
info_messages optional Array<string>

Contains additional information about the request. This field is only returned for successful requests. It may not always be returned, and its content is subject to change.
